These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, montecristo, havana, dunhill
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, d&b, funk, techno
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, mexican, pakistani, russian
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, drawing, fishing, card-games
 1. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 2. the cain-smoker is in an even position##4
 3. the brazilian is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 4. the pakistani is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 5. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 7. the mexican is the havana-smoker##1
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the fan of techno##2
10. the cain-smoker is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
11. the fan of funk is the dunhill-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Cigar          | havana  | cain    | dunhill    | montecristo   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | ambient   | funk       | techno    |
| Nationality   | mexican | brazilian | russian    | pakistani |
| Hobby           | drawing | card-games       | collecting | fishing     |

