.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, bartender, mechanic, accountant
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, drawing, woodworking
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, november, august, january
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, climbing, cycling, volleyball
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the mechanic##1
 4. the bartender is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the dancer##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
 7. the accountant is on the right of the mechanic##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left or far right##3
10. the mechanic is in an odd position##4
11. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Job          | dancer  | bartender    | mechanic     | accountant       |
| Hobby         | drawing | woodworking | baking   | collecting |
| Birthday   | august | april   | november   | january    |
| Sport         | cycling | volleyball  | biathlon | climbing   |

