.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, trike, subway, tram
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, aquamarine, light-blue, red
There are 4 different nationalities: british, egyptian, indonesian, italian
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, hedgehog, mouse
 1. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
 2. the egyptian is the person who likes light-blue##1
 3. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
 4. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 5. the person driving the trike is the person who likes red##1
 6. the person driving the tram is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 7. the owner of the dog is the italian##1
 8. the person who likes red is in an even position##4
 9. the person driving the subway is on the left of the british##1
10. the owner of the dog is the person driving the subway##1
11. the person driving the van is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Transport      | van | subway   | tram    | trike      |
| Color           | light-blue | blood-red | aquamarine | red     |
| Nationality   | egyptian      | italian   | british   | indonesian |
| Pet           | mouse         | dog       | hedgehog  | goat       |

