.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, sprite, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, dubstep, ambient, indie
4 different pets are kept: snake, bird, goat, rat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, parkour, surfing
 1. the person drinking fanta is the fan of gospel##1
 2. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 3. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
 4. the owner of the bird is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 8. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is the owner of the bird##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
11. the person drinking sprite is the fan of indie##1
12. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | water       | sprite   | fanta   | iced-tea   |
| Music-Genre       | dubstep        | indie | gospel    | ambient       |
| Pet      | rat | bird    | goat  | snake |
| Sport      | ice-hockey  | parkour  | cycling | surfing    |

