.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, orange, pineapple, spinach
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, dubstep, house, jazz
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, indian, german, australian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, skiing, snowboarding
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the fan of house is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person eating spinach##2
 3. the german is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 4. the indian is the person eating kiwi##1
 5. the pakistani is on the left or right of the indian##3
 6. the fan of rock is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating orange is the pakistani##1
 8. the fan of house is the indian##1
 9. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
10. the indian is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
12. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | pineapple    | spinach      | kiwi          | orange    |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | jazz       | house | rock |
| Nationality     | australian     | german      | indian     | pakistani |
| Sport   | ice-hockey   | snowboarding | skiing        | cricket   |

