 7. the fan of folk is the firefighter##1
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is the firefighter##1
 9. the colombian is on the far right##1
10. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
