The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, fantasy, sports, zombie
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, papaya, apricot, zucchini
4 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, horse, turtle
 1. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the turtle and the owner of the horse##2
 3. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
 4. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
 7. the owner of the horse is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
 8. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 9. the owner of the dog is between the person eating cauliflower and the person watching fantasy movies##2
10. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
11. the fan of trance is in an even position##4
12. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre         | hip-hop  | electronic    | pop    | trance |
| Movie-Genre   | sports   | epic       | fantasy  | zombie    |
