The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, sunflower, rose, bellflower
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, romance, superhero, crime
 1. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
 2. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 3. the musician is between the person watching crime movies and the person watching western movies##2
 4. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person who growsrose is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
 8. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 9. the social-worker is on the left of the musician##1
10. the dancer is in an even position##4
11. the person who growszinnia is the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |       3        |       4       |
