 9. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
10. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
11. the person eating cucumber is on the far left##1
12. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

