.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, juice, milk
4 different games are played: domino, whist, go, bridge
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, satire, sports, western
City: nizza, prague, marseilles, rome
 1. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 2. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 7. the person playing whist is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
10. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
11. the person watching western movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person playing domino is the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | juice       | hot-chocolate | 7up        | milk        |
| Game         | bridge | go       | domino | whist |
| Movie-Genre   | western     | satire        | mystery    | sports      |
| City         | prague     | marseilles    | rome | nizza   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, house, pop, techno
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, journalist, manager, paramedic
There 4 different types of food: grapes, asparagus, peach, onion
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, helicopter, skateboard
 1. the fan of techno is the person eating peach##1
 2. the person eating peach is between the electrician and the paramedic##2
 3. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3
 4. the person driving the car is on the left of the journalist##1
 5. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 6. the fan of house is the person eating asparagus##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
 8. the paramedic is in an even position##4
 9. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3
10. the electrician is in an even position##4
11. the electrician is on the far right##1
12. the fan of ambient is on the right of the manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | house      | ambient | techno     | pop        |
| Job   | manager | paramedic  | journalist     | electrician |
| Food         | asparagus    | grapes | peach      | onion |
| Transport     | skateboard | car     | helicopter | bike       |

 